    "Nexo Whisper captures on-screen text to understand the context of your voice input, which significantly improves transcription accuracy. Your privacy is important: this data is processed locally and is not stored.": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Nexo Whisper captura el texto en pantalla para entender el contexto de tu voz y mejorar mucho la precisión de la transcripción. Tu privacidad importa: estos datos se procesan localmente y no se guardan."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Nexo Whisper needs Accessibility permission to work reliably across your entire Mac": {
      "localizations": {
