      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Panel de respuesta"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Action buttons": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Botones de acción"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Restore the default chips": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Restaurar los chips por defecto"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Choose which ones you see in the panel, reorder them or create your own.": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Elegí cuáles ves en el panel, ordenalos o creá los tuyos."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Preferred language": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Idioma preferido"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Detect the target language automatically": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Detectar el idioma de destino automáticamente"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If the text is already in your preferred language, it translates to your language; otherwise, to the preferred one. You can still pick another language from the chip.": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Si el texto ya está en tu idioma preferido, lo traduce a tu idioma; si no, al preferido. Igual podés elegir otro idioma desde el chip."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Always translates to the preferred language. You can pick another one from the chip.": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Siempre traduce al idioma preferido. Podés elegir otro puntual desde el chip."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "On non-native Mac apps (Chrome, Slack, Discord, VS Code and others based on Chromium/Electron), due to a macOS limitation, Magic can't detect the text field. To paste the result, tap the **“Replace text”** button in the panel.": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "En apps que no son nativas de Mac (Chrome, Slack, Discord, VS Code y otras basadas en Chromium/Electron), por una limitación del propio macOS, Magic no puede detectar el campo de texto. Para pegar el resultado, tocá el botón **“Reemplazar texto”** del panel."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Actions": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Acciones"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Confirm events without a date before creating": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Confirmar eventos sin fecha antes de crear"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If you ask for an event and no date is detected, it shows a form to set it. The rest of the actions (email, message, map, reminder, event with a date) run directly.": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Si pedís un evento y no se detecta una fecha, muestra un formulario para ponerla. El resto de las acciones (mail, mensaje, mapa, recordatorio, evento con fecha) se ejecutan directo."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Default messaging app": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "App de mensajería por defecto"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "For “send this as a message”. The chosen app's icon appears in the panel.": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Para “mandá esto por mensaje”. El ícono de la app elegida aparece en el panel."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Read text under the cursor with vision (OCR)": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Leer texto bajo el cursor con visión (OCR)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When an app doesn't expose its text (terminals, images, PDFs), Magic captures the area under the cursor and reads it with Apple's on-device recognition. Free and private.": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cuando una app no expone su texto (terminales, imágenes, PDFs), Magic captura la zona bajo el cursor y la lee con reconocimiento on-device de Apple. Gratis y privado."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The panel closes on its own": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El panel se cierra solo"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Never": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Nunca"
          }
        }
      }
    },
